0.1.0.name: wordpress/empire-avenue-tools
0.1.0.description:
Add Empire Avenue features to your blog. This plugin will automatically convert (e)TICKER on your blog to a link to the user's page on EA.

Customize the behavior by editing the empireavenue.js file. See the Eavify documentation for more details.

The plugin also features the EA badge as a widget.
